title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - UK Film studios -Warner Bros Pinewood
description:
In this video we will look at two film studios which have been made available as a mod by on of the community members. Both Warner Bros and Pinewood are now available for MSFS 2020. The sceneries are both photogrammetry quality but you shouldn't fly to low over them. Both studios are very close to other airports and are located on the west side of London. 

If you also want to give this mod a try download your own copy via the links below:

https://flightsim.to/download/pinewood-and-warner-bros-uk-film-studios/22602
